If at any time you need to drop to console for any reason or any errors or any bugs or any broken packages that need repaired or just anything that you need actual admin route access for you drop to console and to do it  on some machines, it is F1 and on some machines it is F2 and then you should be in console in the command line and all you see is terminal

And then you should be up and going with all the features and functionality of Ubuntu server and all the features and functionality of Ubuntu studio with all appropriate packages in a sleek, familiar GUI and ready for all your creative needs 

